{"tid":235902,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人分手後愈來愈自卑？","createTime":"2017-05-09T10:37:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-09T16:55:04.000Z","uid":58335,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a87879f4f2b76300b7f18afb56ac317b4c45a977","tid":235902,"uid":58335,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T10:37:46.000Z","msg":"佢真係好完美，曾經同到佢真係一時幸運<br />\n到佢走左，同左第二個一齊<br />\n<br />\n就覺得自己更垃圾，無錢，無樣咩都冇<br />\n做咩都提唔起勁，更加唔想再識女仔，即使只係做朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我知好多女仔都唔鍾意冇自信既男仔，但真係控制唔到，冇辦法<br />\n可能毒撚真係最忌有自信<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6abb942bd95c29a8e6f4a3561abc4fcd824e67b","tid":235902,"uid":17492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T10:38:23.000Z","msg":"有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea4774c2cff99ce11681d9e0e61c4af957b38492","tid":235902,"uid":106070,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T10:42:49.000Z","msg":"屌尻你，有無攪撚錯呀<br />\n因為分手而自卑，咁樣有閪用咩<br />\n衰左咪衰左， 分左咪溝過第個囉"},{"pid":"3ced46364447432254dcdae69f5d4ad17843e6d9","tid":235902,"uid":104232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T10:48:23.000Z","msg":"呢個有一個垃圾 <br />\n依家無哂自信<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75c81fa6ce24397d9888fb05c01097243842b6a7","tid":235902,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T11:00:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌尻你，有無攪撚錯呀<br />\n因為分手而自卑，咁樣有閪用咩<br />\n衰左咪衰左， 分左咪溝過第個囉</blockquote><br />\n因為好似次次都係我比人違棄<br />\n明知自己其他野唔掂<br />\n就已經特別對佢地好<br />\n點知最後都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好驚再有下一次都係咁，唔敢諗下次<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba80cbe87450c74ef5a34b129ceec2adedf64c10","tid":235902,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T11:01:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢個有一個垃圾 <br />\n依家無哂自信<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n人生已完<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8781146da0e1df79d8b767aeaf8566245c58fe9b","tid":235902,"uid":18143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T11:02:53.000Z","msg":"其他事都冇影響，係講到拍拖溝女會迴避"},{"pid":"b7edb561776e4e54deee1a94e5733feeac430cee","tid":235902,"uid":18845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T11:02:55.000Z","msg":"離開你以後 我會習慣自卑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"260b255f88bacaa0ba936f290f4800804cb590b6","tid":235902,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T11:33:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其他事都冇影響，係講到拍拖溝女會迴避</blockquote><br />\n啱，我都係<br />\n同埋有時會拎佢同其他女比較<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57226f1dafa3afbea827f4b3a5a7617617ffa647","tid":235902,"uid":30788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T11:33:54.000Z","msg":"me"},{"pid":"7d9e50d8d42b8c9811b0fcd8e83f39495eddc8d0","tid":235902,"uid":6957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T12:59:51.000Z","msg":"冇記錯你ex搵返ex<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？"},{"pid":"1a9cf8f3140c0b4944d638eb16b705e4a36fc91c","tid":235902,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T13:20:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇記錯你ex搵返ex<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？</blockquote><br />\n掛住即，冇搵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但好似有新仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9d180f9de5f5420fb4a98a52158a4bc43346797","tid":235902,"uid":111873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T13:31:06.000Z","msg":"未搵啱人啫<br />\n<br />\n我同我前度分手之後都係咁諗<br />\n過左幾年之後先遇到而家個個<br />\n<br />\n其實係好多人眼中佢細過我識野少過我<br />\n但遍遍就對我好好 好錫我<br />\n<br />\n鐘意一個人可以好簡單<br />\n但千祈要有底線 無止境咁遷就最後只會令其中一方頂唔順<br />\n<br />\n加油啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb7785c4901276be044c11e4f1ce50d2955d4784","tid":235902,"uid":10141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T13:45:20.000Z","msg":"一直都自卑開<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3a27b59530a495ef48e5ab0fe24a8a33ce13839","tid":235902,"uid":27251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T13:50:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c856677660c5366bafb88de0e194b380480cf8f4","tid":235902,"uid":20302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T13:52:19.000Z","msg":"初初分手果陣自信心插到谷底<br />\n<br />\n慢慢諗通左  再係咁只會無限頹  <br />\n<br />\n所以要活得更好"},{"pid":"a891538557c0221910b9b835c6ec7a291e855a4f","tid":235902,"uid":27416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T13:53:28.000Z","msg":"same ar bro<br />\n諗返真係唔知點解會揀我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d56012f1848788ee4b008f1f671fc686cd7af07","tid":235902,"uid":6989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T14:01:49.000Z","msg":"所以分左手後, 多左時間做自己野, 儲多左錢. 善用時間同金錢去增值自己, 令自己更吸引, 唔好再自卑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2045558236be9202208fd4df3383ea74f6fbccaf","tid":235902,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T14:47:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>所以分左手後, 多左時間做自己野, 儲多左錢. 善用時間同金錢去增值自己, 令自己更吸引, 唔好再自卑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有時明知應該點做<br />\n但心理硬係覺得比唔上人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"088a23669aa82f5f7bfaa0ddabe8379d6b1d830a","tid":235902,"uid":18456,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T14:48:58.000Z","msg":"你又吾好甘諗 您都一定有吸引力 俾啲信心自己丫"},{"pid":"e46577ed08549b7c3f870e2fa6a0dd9989920769","tid":235902,"uid":18456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T14:49:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>所以分左手後, 多左時間做自己野, 儲多左錢. 善用時間同金錢去增值自己, 令自己更吸引, 唔好再自卑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有時明知應該點做<br />\n但心理硬係覺得比唔上人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n比賽只會令自己更難受。加油丫"},{"pid":"a1a4dcfe0514262c77534714926a443aaab35d0e","tid":235902,"uid":104232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T14:52:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>未搵啱人啫<br />\n<br />\n我同我前度分手之後都係咁諗<br />\n過左幾年之後先遇到而家個個<br />\n<br />\n其實係好多人眼中佢細過我識野少過我<br />\n但遍遍就對我好好 好錫我<br />\n<br />\n鐘意一個人可以好簡單<br />\n但千祈要有底線 無止境咁遷就最後只會令其中一方頂唔順<br />\n<br />\n加油啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屌 其實我仲掛住佢 不過佢玩玩下既心態 當我無到<br />\n傷心死 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78471bb34f7f15ec5c6c6c3e4c3022a8b485f7a9","tid":235902,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T16:55:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}